        <h1>Early closing Mondays to Thursdays on Victoria line</h1>
        <div class="content-page-press-release">
        13 July 2007
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="main-and-aside r">
    <div class="main" role="main">



<div class="pull-quote">
        <div class="quote-body">"While planning the programme we have taken care to cause minimum disruption to passengers"</div>
        <div class="quote-footer">
            <div class="quotee-name">Howard Collins</div>
            <div class="quotee-job-title">Deputy Chief Operating Officer</div>
        </div>
