<li>Tube Lines is responsible for the maintenance and renewal of Jubilee, Northern and Piccadilly lines</li>
<li>Metronet Rail BCV is responsible for the maintenance and renewal of the Bakerloo, Central, Victoria and Waterloo &amp; City lines</li>
<li>Metronet Rail SSL is responsible for the maintenance and renewal of the sub surface lines - the Circle, District, Hammersmith &amp; City, Metropolitan and East London lines<br></li></ul>

     

        
        
        
